Package no.geosoft.jtimeseries

Class TimeSeries

java.lang.Object
no.geosoft.jtimeseries.TimeSeries
public final class TimeSeries extends Object
Class representing the content of one TimeSeries.JSON entry. A TimeSeries consists of a header, signal definitions, and signal data.
Author:
Jacob Dreyer

    • setStep

      public void setStep(Double step)
      Set the regular step of the index curve of this log.
      Parameters:
      step - Step to set. Null to indicate unknown or that the index is irregular. If the log set is time based, the step should be the number of milliseconds between samples.
